Rand::MersenneTwister Version 1.0.0
========================

DESCRIPTION
-----------

Context driven Mersenne Twister-based PRNG.  Allows you to have multiple
concurrent PRNGs all individually seeded.

PREREQUISITES
-------------

Perl 5.

INSTALLATION
------------

1.  perl Makefile.PL
2.  make test
3.  make install

